column5: The wind has been nice to us the last few times out, we were catching them on Spinnerbaits, Swimbaits, Drop Shot & Tubes the gar moved in one day there was hundreds in the school had one grab a swimbait but when I got it to the boat it opened it's mouth and swam away, so we didn't fish for them long, also thousands of gizzard shad, a couple guys we talked to have been catching some walleye & a few brown over at Bruce B, mostly early or late & at night Richard
you guys are champs.  Hey what was the water temp.  if you know thanks.
Water been 69 to 72 at the out flow Richard
